---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
    <section style="
        width: 100%;
        background: #0f172a;
        margin-top: -2rem; /* Pull flush against the site header navigation */
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        align-items: center;
        border-bottom: 4px solid #2563eb;
    ">
        <div style="padding: 4rem 3rem 5rem 4rem;">
            <span style="
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.12rem;
                color: #38bdf8;
                display: block;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            ">Advancing Knowledge • Societal Impact</span>
            
            <h1 style="
                color: #ffffff;
                font-size: 2.8rem;
                font-weight: 800;
                line-height: 1.25;
                margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
                letter-spacing: -0.02rem;
            ">Integrating Complex Synthesis, Methodology and Translational Science</h1>
            
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <a href="/publications" style="
                    background: #2563eb;
                    color: white;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
                    border-radius: 4px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
                ">Learn About Our Research</a>
                <a href="/team" style="
                    background: transparent;
                    color: #ffffff;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
                    border-radius: 4px;
                    font-weight: 600;
                    font-size: 0.9rem;
                    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
                    text-transform: uppercase;
                    letter-spacing: 0.05rem;
                ">Meet The Group</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="
            background: #0f172a; 
            height: 100%; 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        ">
            <img src="/images/dark_network.png" alt="Multi-omic network simulation" style="
                max-width: 90%;
                max-height: 420px;
                object-fit: contain;
            " />
        </div>
    </section>

    <section style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700;">Driving Research Forward</h2>
            <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 1.1rem;">We are a dedicated team of scientists seeking to advance fundamental knowledge and impact society.</p>
        </div>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2.5rem;">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="color: #2563eb; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Computational Epidemiology</h3>
                <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">Characterizing complex molecular signatures of the exposome, including cross-layer implications of environmental and social determinants.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="color: #2563eb; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Biostatistics</h3>
                <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">Developing novel, computationally robust stability selection methodologies engineered for high-dimensional multi-omic array testing parameters.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <h3 style="color: #2563eb; font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Translational Science</h3>
                <p style="color: #475569; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.6;">Leveraging massive population biobank data registries to explore underlying biological mechanisms and translate data directly into public health frameworks.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>